data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home! As you enter, you are greeted by a foyer that leads to the living room, featuring a stone corner fireplace and hardwood flooring with crown molding. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with espresso stained cabinets, granite counter tops, center island, corner windows above the sink, and stainless steel appliances. The adjacent dining area has a bay window and an atrium door that opens to the oversized, covered patio. The master retreat boasts a tiered ceiling with a lighted fan and a beautifully appointed bath with a whirlpool tub flanked by walk-in closets and a separate shower enclosure, as well as a cultured marble topped vanity. The other three bedrooms have raised ceilings and generous closet space, and the hall bathroom offers tiled flooring and a tub.This home offers many extra amenities, including carpet-less interior, a unique wood accented ceiling in the dining area, security sprinkler systems, and no neighbors to the rear. This amazing home is located in a convenient location, close to Harker Heights Community Park and only about 10 miles from Fort Cavazos. With all of these features, this home is sure to please!
